item.title: Notes
item.description:
For browsing the wiki normally, it is useful to have all the information of one specific game together. For this, each game has a navigation bar. However, when editing content or adding information, it's generally more useful for the pages to be categorized depending on that pages context (e.g. Location Types, Image Types, ), and then using lower-order subcategories or name prefixes when separating categories between games is necessary.
In this example hierarchy, not every category is worked out fully. For generations only 6thGen, for Games only MHWilds, for Weapons only Great Sword, and for Attributes only Fire are worked out.
